body_html:
Some perf numbers for stock builds and and builds without __force_inline.
There is some impact, maybe 10% on average - details below.
This is from a little benchmark tool that runs some simple fc, lstm, conv nets and takes numbers for training and eval. The eval numbers (ms units, the tool runs 1000 and takes the average) are worse than training.
The diff column shows the change compared to a stock build.

net name env time(sec) diff% evaltime(ms) diff%
conv stock vs2015.3 809.27   1.4375  
conv nofi vs2015.3 844.64 4.37060561 1.5937 10.86609
conv stock vs2017.15.4 783.12   1.4063  
conv nofi vs2017.15.4 824.65 5.30314639 1.5469 9.997867
fc stock vs2015.3 178.28   0.3281  
fc nofi vs2015.3 194.4 9.04195647 0.3906 19.04907
fc stock vs2017.15.4 180.66   0.3437  
fc nofi vs2017.15.4 185.48 2.66799513 0.3437 0
lstm stock vs2015.3 176.34   1.8906  
lstm nofi vs2015.3 202.7 14.9483951 2.2728 20.2158
lstm stock vs2017.15.4 182.29   1.9471  
lstm nofi vs2017.15.4 197.25 8.2067036 1.9063 -2.09542

body:
Some perf numbers for stock builds and and builds without __force_inline. 
There is some impact, maybe 10% on average - details below.
This is from a little benchmark tool that runs some simple fc, lstm, conv nets and takes numbers for training and eval. The eval numbers (ms units, the tool runs 1000 and takes the average) are worse than training.
The diff column shows the change compared to a stock build.

net | name | env | time(sec) | diff% | evaltime(ms) | diff%
-- | -- | -- | -- | -- | -- | --
conv | stock | vs2015.3 | 809.27 |   | 1.4375 |  
conv | nofi | vs2015.3 | 844.64 | 4.37060561 | 1.5937 | 10.86609
conv | stock | vs2017.15.4 | 783.12 |   | 1.4063 |  
conv | nofi | vs2017.15.4 | 824.65 | 5.30314639 | 1.5469 | 9.997867
fc | stock | vs2015.3 | 178.28 |   | 0.3281 |  
fc | nofi | vs2015.3 | 194.4 | 9.04195647 | 0.3906 | 19.04907
fc | stock | vs2017.15.4 | 180.66 |   | 0.3437 |  
fc | nofi | vs2017.15.4 | 185.48 | 2.66799513 | 0.3437 | 0
lstm | stock | vs2015.3 | 176.34 |   | 1.8906 |  
lstm | nofi | vs2015.3 | 202.7 | 14.9483951 | 2.2728 | 20.2158
lstm | stock | vs2017.15.4 | 182.29 |   | 1.9471 |  
lstm | nofi | vs2017.15.4 | 197.25 | 8.2067036 | 1.9063 | -2.09542
